creator: Hytch LLC
descriptionHtml:
Hytch
Noun, verb;
Carbon zero commuting, anywhere in America.

Contribute to the nation’s largest carbon offset program that you can participate in for FREE anytime you commute. The Hych app allows you to track your transit and earn carbon offset for your emissions. Whether you are walking, biking, carpooling, vanpooling, taking public transit, riding an e-scooter, or using Uber or Lyft simply tap the “Let’s Hytch” button and start tracking your trip.

Think of it like a FitBit for your transportation and instead of a healthy body, you contribute to a healthy planet.

How to use Hytch:
Tap the “Let’s Hytch” button and select if you are traveling solo or with friends
Invite your friends, family, and coworkers to Hytch if they are with you
Choose your mode of transportation
Track your miles and see your impact
Earn offsets that make every Hytch carbon neutral
Redeem cash rewards earned in sponsored markets*

*Sponsored markets are areas where cash rewards are available thanks to companies who care

- Added motion and whirligigs to fancy up ads
- Improved rewards engine intelligence: Now umpty-times more smarter than were it before it was

title: Hytch Rewards

creator: Hytch LLC
descriptionHtml:
Imagine you planted a tree for every fifty miles you drive, walk or bike - anywhere in the USA? Use the Hytch app to claim that reward. It works when you use public transit, take a scooter or vanpool, and it's always more rewarding when you share rides. Eco friendly employers use Hytch to deliver cash incentives for carpooling to work and participating in mobile mentoring programs with new employees. It's a great way to beat climate change, no matter how you get there, and it's free!

Think of it like a FitBit for your transportation where instead of a healthy body, you contribute to a healthy planet. If it's convenient, help shape the culture at work by sharing rides, leveraging commute time to build deeper and more positive relationships as you get to know co-workers or new associates.

HOW TO USE HYTCH:

Tap the "Let's Hytch" button to select if you are traveling solo or with friends.
Earn more rewards by inviting coworkers, friends or family to join you in a Hytch when traveling with you.
Select your mode of transportation and start that trip. That's it!
Learn about your reduced emissions, plant your forest and redeem cash rewards in sponsored markets, which is anywhere cash rewards are available thanks to companies who care about their team and your community.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Open a trip you're curious about in trip history
- Scroll down and click on "Contact Support"
- Fill in the "Message" field + make sure all other information provided is correct
- Hit "Send Message"
- Verify your email in your profile
- Verification now required to cash out
- Opt in for notifications to learn about new rewards available.
- Overlapping banners are now a thing of the past
- Wallopped a small handful of other unwelcome critters
